@carto4028 Those were the crews of military ships and space stations. They can be replaced since there are hundreds to thousands of qualified people to replace them.

This show has the *leaders of a near extinct* species making a decision that puts their species at major risk. People who cannot be replaced with how few people are left.

Those two situations do not compare.

