@BrandiDandelion Try Enterprise again.  It holds up a lot better than I thought.

When it originally aired, I thought it was garbage (theme song sucked) but I checked it out recently because nu-trek is an abomination... and NOW I appreciate Enterprise for what it was.  It was the last Star Trek with INTEGRITY.  

I was just burned out on Trek when it originally aired, and had no idea how much I would miss it, in the coming years.
